      "modified": "1970-01-01T00:00:00.034Z",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "The machine reads the page aloud, letter for letter. Under the cipher reading you are hearing enciphered speech; under the grille reading you are hearing the rhythm a table-and-overlay produces; under the abjad reading you are hearing a real language you simply don't know. Same sound, three claims. [the page it reads aloud](https://archie.demo/voynich/) (03 §4 cross-link AV→image f18v; `archie:` ref resolves to the voynich exhibit. A note-precise `archie:voynich/#/a/<logicalId>` target awaits a stable R2 note id — human/Studio follow-up.)",
          "purpose": "commenting"
        }
      ],
      "archie:hasHistory": "https://archie.demo/voynich/annotations/history/0000000012NNEE2QZS03TQVZCX.json"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://archie.demo/voynich/annotations/0000000013WM8JQF4NZDPEX0DY/v1",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "target": {
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "source": "https://archie.demo/voynich/canvas/o12",
        "selector": {
          "type": "FragmentSelector",
